<br>
Discoveries:<br>
<br>
Pop Time: Approx 30hours<br>
Clear Port in Side to Stream: Approx 5-7 Hours<br>
Clear Entire Plane: Probably a 2 day raid similar to PoS or 2 Raid parties in 1 day<br>
Mezzing: According to Bulgint (sorry if I misspelled your name) mobs past stream can not be mezzes.  Makes crowd ctrl harder.<br>
Boss and Minor Boss: My understanding is plane must be cleared before attacking Tunar.  It appears she Summons (not calls like Cazic, but Summons) every mob in the zone to her side.  So, you would need to empty the plane prior to re-pops.<br>
<br>
Ideas:<br>
<br>
We have choice #1:  PoG follows same standard reservation rules as Fear and Hate<br>
<br>
We have choice #2:  Due to the size of PoG, a lot feel 2 or more raiding parties can occur at once.<br>
<br>
We have choice #3:  A combination of #1 and #2.<br>
<br>
More choices? Post them.<br>
<br>
Unknowns to me and probably others:<br>
<br>
1) Spawn time of PoG<br>
2) Can PoG be cleared from top to bottom in 8-10hours with 1 raid party OR before zone repop.<br>
3) How large of a raid party is needed to kill the boss and sub bosses?<br>
<br>
Other questions? Post them.<br>
<br>
My first thoughts to start discussion:  Clearing PoG during the week would be hard due to its size.  So Monday - Friday 2 raid parties can be in PoG.  On Saturday and Sunday 1 raiding party.  There would be some type of dividing line.  Maybe everything north of x axis 1000 is party 1, south is party 2.  Or, maybe it's just you pull it first you get it rule. <br>
<br>
Post your thoughts, questions, ideas and I'll change the info here as ideas start to come in. <p><b>Redspine Bladeslinger - 56th Myrmidon</b><br>
